      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. This unit boasts a healthy VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring the chassis handles the 333hp output with precision. The limited-slip differential provides optimal power delivery out of corners, while the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications. Well-maintained and performance-ready, this is a tactile, analog driving experience for the discerning collector.",
