    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a 2017 Lexus RX 350 finished in a timeless Eminent White Pearl with a Parchment leather interior. This vehicle has been maintained to a high standard and presents beautifully, though it shows the honest character of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, with the only notable imperfections being a few small stone chips on the leading edge of the hood and a minor 1-inch scuff on the lower passenger-side rear bumper. The 20-inch alloy wheels are clean, with no significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather upholstery is soft and free of punctures or heavy bolster wear, and the wood trim is vibrant. All power accessories, including the panoramic sunroof, 12.3-inch navigation display, and heated/ventilated front seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is excellent. It features a comprehensive service log with its most recent 60,000-mile major service already completed, including a fresh oil change, cabin air filter replacement, and a brake system flush. The Michelin tires provide a quiet ride with ample tread depth remaining. This is a non-smoker, garage-kept SUV that comes with two sets of keys, the original owner's manuals, and all-weather floor mats.",
