    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained to ensure consistent performance and driver satisfaction. Its refined exterior is complemented by a well-preserved interior, reflecting a history of responsible ownership. Mechanical integrity remains paramount, offering a seamless driving experience for the discerning professional. This offering represents a superb balance of luxury and utility, providing exceptional value for those who demand reliability without compromise.",
      "price": 34500.0,
