      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super reliable, and has been well-taken care of over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 33500.0,
